{"tid":1305964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁美芬：有議員辦公室鎖匙遺失感不安全　林卓廷：心虛","createTime":"2019-07-11T03:49:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T04:40:15.000Z","uid":212626,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ff5ce7dc59ddc0287053271f6e7442b6ca6c2aa7","tid":1305964,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:49:07.000Z","msg":"立法會上午8時解除紅色警示，立法會辦公室樓重開，議員、職員和記者可返回大樓工作。<br />\n<br />\n經民聯九龍西議員梁美芬指出，大部分議員辦公室的鎖匙現時仍然遺失，有<span style=\"color: red;\">不安全的感覺</span>，要聽秘書處再報告遺失的鎖匙會否影響相關樓層。<br />\n<br />\n立法會亦通知議員，指大樓保安控制室及保安系統仍在維修，包括6樓至10樓的視像對講機、議員辦事處內的求救警鐘，及進出控制系統仍未完全修復。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨林卓廷反駁稱，立法會大樓附近有警員巡邏，建制派議員感覺不安全是基於<span style=\"color: red;\">心虛</span>，又反問傳媒在大樓附近採訪有否覺得不安全。<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷又指出，近日各區出現由反修例人士設置的「連儂牆」，得悉有建制派支持者破壞標語甚至攻擊保護「連儂牆」的市民，他要求警方嚴肅調查，他將會聯絡民主黨各區區議員，假如發生事故會立即前往協助。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2188904/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2188904%2F&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnTvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=f1273c31\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2188904/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2188906/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2188906%2F&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnTvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=22340992\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2188906/</a>"},{"pid":"3cbb23100b844f144be8b6af27a57055d046a380","tid":1305964,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:51:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0df23034c1e7187e4c5ca8f4976999eaea2c91aa","tid":1305964,"uid":73826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:55:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回612暴動定義